n=A.b(["\u0110\u0103ng k\xfd v\xe0 \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng","X\xe1c minh ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng qua m\xe3 OTP","T\xecm ki\u1ebfm danh s\xe1ch cho thu\xea t\u1ea1i c\xe1c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\xf3 s\u1eb5n","B\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc n\xe2ng cao: lo\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n (chung c\u01b0 mini, nh\xe0 \u1edf gh\xe9p, homestay, v.v.), lo\u1ea1i ph\xf2ng (ph\xf2ng t\u1eafm chung/ri\xeang, s\u1ed1 ph\xf2ng ng\u1ee7/ph\xf2ng kh\xe1ch, ph\xf2ng \u0111\u01a1n, v.v.), kho\u1ea3ng gi\xe1 v\xe0 ti\u1ec7n nghi (Wi-Fi, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\xf2a, m\xe1y gi\u1eb7t, v.v.)","Qu\u1ea3n l\xfd ph\xf2ng c\u1ee7a t\xf4i, bao g\u1ed3m ph\xf2ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\xe0 \u0111\xe3 thu\xea","Thu\xea ph\xf2ng v\xe0 nh\u1eadn ph\xf2ng (ph\xf2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o b\u1edfi Ahome Pro; ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eadn ph\xf2ng)","B\xe1o c\xe1o s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 cho ch\u1ee7 nh\xe0/ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu","H\xf3a \u0111\u01a1n thanh to\xe1n ph\xf2ng"],p)
q=A.kp(A.b([a1,a2],p),A.b([a3,a4],p),"Ahome is a rental platform that enables users to find, filter, and book apartments directly from property owners in Vietnam, with features such as OTP authentication, advanced search, room management, and issue reporting.","Ahome l\xe0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho thu\xea gi\xfap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng t\xecm ki\u1ebfm, l\u1ecdc v\xe0 \u0111\u1eb7t ph\xf2ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb ch\u1ee7 nh\xe0 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, v\u1edbi c\xe1c t\xednh n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 x\xe1c th\u1ef1c OTP, t\xecm ki\u1ebfm n\xe2ng cao, qu\u1ea3n l\xfd ph\xf2ng v\xe0 b\xe1o c\xe1o s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1.","assets/ahome.png",o,n,"Ahome","https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/homevn-tr%E1%BB%8D-ch%C3%ADnh-ch%E1%BB%A7/id6736515000?l=vi","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=vn.xtel.ahome.timtro&hl=vi",g,a0,q)
n=A.b(["User registration and authentication (OTP verification)","Building and room management (by type, category, and name)","Room billing management (rent, utilities, and service fees) with invoice delivery","Room details and contract management (deposit creation, contract creation, renewal, and cancellation) with tenant check-in and payment confirmation","Handle reports and issues from tenants, with maintenance status updates (pending, in progress, completed)","Monthly statistics on payment status (fully paid, partially paid, unpaid), room status (occupied, vacant, expiring), and maintenance tracking","Payment information and bank account management","Create and publish rental listings for Ahome users"],p)
o=A.b(["\u0110\u0103ng k\xfd v\xe0 x\xe1c th\u1ef1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng (x\xe1c minh OTP)","Qu\u1ea3n l\xfd t\xf2a nh\xe0 v\xe0 ph\xf2ng (theo lo\u1ea1i, danh m\u1ee5c v\xe0 t\xean)","Qu\u1ea3n l\xfd h\xf3a \u0111\u01a1n ph\xf2ng (ti\u1ec1n thu\xea, \u0111i\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc v\xe0 ph\xed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5) v\u1edbi g\u1eedi h\xf3a \u0111\u01a1n","Chi ti\u1ebft ph\xf2ng v\xe0 qu\u1ea3n l\xfd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng (t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc, t\u1ea1o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, gia h\u1ea1n v\xe0 h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf) v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn ph\xf2ng v\xe0 x\xe1c nh\u1eadn thanh to\xe1n","X\u1eed l\xfd b\xe1o c\xe1o v\xe0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi thu\xea, v\u1edbi c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i b\u1ea3o tr\xec (ch\u1edd x\u1eed l\xfd, \u0111ang x\u1eed l\xfd, ho\xe0n th\xe0nh)","Th\u1ed1ng k\xea h\xe0ng th\xe1ng v\u1ec1 t\xecnh tr\u1ea1ng thanh to\xe1n (\u0111\xe3 thanh to\xe1n, thanh to\xe1n m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n, ch\u01b0a thanh to\xe1n), tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i ph\xf2ng (\u0111\xe3 thu\xea, tr\u1ed1ng, s\u1eafp h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n) v\xe0 theo d\xf5i b\u1ea3o tr\xec","Qu\u1ea3n l\xfd th\xf4ng tin thanh to\xe1n v\xe0 t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n ng\xe2n h\xe0ng","T\u1ea1o v\xe0 \u0111\u0103ng tin cho thu\xea cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng Ahome"],p)
