n=A.as2(A.b([q,m,l,A.kp(A.b(["Key contributor (~50% of the project)","Refactored and structured the codebase, applied best practices in state management, and organized the project using corebase and melos","Developed news, events, and legal handbook features","Implemented survey and voting system","Developed authentic product guide features","Deploy the application to CHplay and Appstore."],p),A.b(["\u0110\xf3ng g\xf3p ch\xednh (~50% d\u1ef1 \xe1n)","T\xe1i c\u1ea5u tr\xfac v\xe0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c codebase, \xe1p d\u1ee5ng best practices trong qu\u1ea3n l\xfd tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i, v\xe0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c d\u1ef1 \xe1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng corebase v\xe0 melos","Ph\xe1t tri\u1ec3n t\xednh n\u0103ng tin t\u1ee9c, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\xe0 s\u1ed5 tay ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt","Tri\u1ec3n khai h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u1ea3o s\xe1t v\xe0 b\xecnh ch\u1ecdn","Ph\xe1t tri\u1ec3n t\xednh n\u0103ng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m x\xe1c th\u1ef1c","Tri\u1ec3n khai \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng l\xean CHplay v\xe0 Appstore."],p),"The \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi ti\xeau d\xf9ng\u201d app provides knowledge, news, and guidance to protect the rights and legitimate interests of consumers. Users can easily access essential consumer rights, safety alerts, and the latest updates from the Vietnam Consumer Protection Association.","\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi ti\xeau d\xf9ng\u201d cung c\u1ea5p ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, tin t\u1ee9c v\xe0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quy\u1ec1n v\xe0 l\u1ee3i \xedch h\u1ee3p ph\xe1p c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\xeau d\xf9ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng c\xf3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\xe0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\xe1c quy\u1ec1n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, c\u1ea3nh b\xe1o an to\xe0n v\xe0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb H\u1ed9i B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\xeau d\xf9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam.","assets/nguoitieudung.png",o,k,"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\xeau d\xf9ng","https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/ng%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Di-ti%C3%AAu-d%C3%B9ng/id6737721544?l=vi","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=vn.org.nguoitieudung&hl=vi",g,a5,n)],j),new A.B9(500,20,20,1.5),new A.b3(0,20,0,20),B.jY,!0)
