m=A.kp(A.b(["Maintained and enhanced the mobile application.","Contributed approximately 28% of the overall project development.","Updated UI and business logic based on evolving requirements.","Refactored legacy code, applied best practices for state management, and improved app responsiveness.","Optimized the video lesson module to prevent crashes and ensure smooth playback.","Developed user interaction features for community posts.","Implemented Phoenix account upgrade and payment functionality."],p),A.b(["B\u1ea3o tr\xec v\xe0 n\xe2ng c\u1ea5p \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng mobile.","\u0110\xf3ng g\xf3p kho\u1ea3ng 28% ph\xe1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \xe1n.","C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt UI v\xe0 logic nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 theo y\xeau c\u1ea7u thay \u0111\u1ed5i.","T\xe1i c\u1ea5u tr\xfac m\xe3 c\u0169, \xe1p d\u1ee5ng best practices qu\u1ea3n l\xfd tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i v\xe0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i.","T\u1ed1i \u01b0u module b\xe0i gi\u1ea3ng video \u0111\u1ec3 tr\xe1nh crash v\xe0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ph\xe1t l\u1ea1i m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\xe0.","Ph\xe1t tri\u1ec3n t\xednh n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\xe1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng cho b\xe0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng.","Tri\u1ec3n khai n\xe2ng c\u1ea5p t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n Phoenix v\xe0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng thanh to\xe1n."],p),"The application enables Phoenix users and students to connect, learn, and engage within a community-driven platform, offering features such as social networking, mentorship content, events, numerology insights, and marketing courses.","\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng gi\xfap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng v\xe0 h\u1ecdc vi\xean Phoenix k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i, h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\xe0 tham gia trong n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ea1ng x\xe3 h\u1ed9i, n\u1ed9i dung mentor, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, th\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc v\xe0 kh\xf3a h\u1ecdc marketing.","assets/phoenixcamp.png",l,h,"Phoenix - camp","https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/phoenix-ng%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Di-d%E1%BA%ABn-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/id6504493368?l=vi","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=vn.phoenixcamp.mobile&hl=vi",g,a5,m)
